WRAP: PRO14 - Week 5

02 Nov 2019, 22:00

Cape Town - Dates, fixtures, results and match reports for this weekend's PRO14 tournament.

FRIDAY, NOVEMBER 1:

Ulster 22-7 Zebre 
Leinster 50-15 Dragons
Glasgow Warriors 50-0 Southern Kings 

SATURDAY, NOVEMBER 2:

Llanelli Scarlets 17-13 Cheetahs
Ospreys 10-20 Connacht 
Benetton Rugby 18-16 Edinburgh
Cardiff Blues v Munster - 21:35
